以叫支那蝗一齊抵制麥記"},{"pid":"10e65ea17a2e34467421797ad17475e50f5087a6","tid":1503773,"uid":231055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:02:01.000Z","msg":"我地今場運動證明左好多野，<br />\n證明左中聯辦治港<br />\n證明左警黑合作<br />\n證明左武警扮黑警<br />\n證明黑警會扮示威者<br />\n證明左狗鐵監控直駁狗總<br />\n再俾你地證明監控燈柱直駁大陸<br />\n仲證明左好多野！<br />\n然後呢？沒有然係，證明咁多野做咩？ <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢場運動唔係捉錯處，唔係搵得越多就會贏。港共根本一步一步謀殺緊香港人。</span></span><br />\n場運動根本入左死局，示威者剩係識不停漫無目的咁上街示威，白白犧牲，然後港共就加強打壓。<br />\n咁樣係唔會贏架！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>只有撃中港共弱點，先有資格同佢平起平坐講數。</strong></span></span><br />\n只有港共一跪，所有野先有機會平反，要撤監控唔係去發現佢監控，然後推低支燈柱，係要去解決個源頭，否則我地同大陸人有咩分別？<br />\n大陸人一樣知中共幾醜惡，但佢地推翻唔到，證明到個政府有幾邪惡係無用架！<br />\n明明已經有咁清晰嘅弱點暴露左出黎，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>機場就係港共春袋</span></span></strong><br />\n唔去打佢痛處，依然每星期動員去上街，叫叫口號拍拍手散水就可以？<br />\n然後再俾人捉幾十人去審？<br />\n旅客緊要定我地香港人緊要？<br />\n係咪要犧牲晒年輕一代，犧牲佢地健康，<br />\n犧牲佢地健全，最後犧牲佢地性命先滿足？<br />\n尋求國際協助？別再發夢了，國際間只有利益，沒有免費的正義。請撫心自問，你地有關注敘利亞，阿富汗平民每日嘅苦況？睡覺中突然遭到空襲，可能一睡就不醒。<br />\n有關注北韓，新彊嘅打壓？佢地人民每日都生活係監控同操縱底下。<br />\n你，香港人在承受的，算什麼？憑什麼要國際援助你？你以為依家受嘅打壓好嚴重？比我地嚴重嘅人比比皆是，香港人只有自救才有出路。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">機場清場等同解放軍入城，大家唔係好想佢出老解？機場清場一樣做到同樣效果，到時就俾到子彈外國勢力支持香港人</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e32e57688cc848384efbc271bbec926d05c3443d","tid":1503773,"uid":53361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d446a242679029cbcc8423d8afdff5a56f7b25d3","tid":1503773,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eeeb71abbde70ce9144f5f9327dd6bc564a1c136","tid":1503773,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e99e5c84865e1338a85201d2207b378c7bb452ba","tid":1503773,"uid":53361,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:38:47.000Z","msg":"仲用緊M記個招牌<br />\n形象既野<br />\n係美國好似好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:39:47.000Z","msg":"賣撚左佢可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:00:04.000Z","msg":"賣經營權姐 有時限"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:08:48.000Z","msg":"唔識咩經營權<br />\n但見佢仲用緊M記個招牌<br />\n總公司應該都要責任回答下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e28a1d14c322e455fbe2f6af7acdca23a80ca29","tid":1503773,"uid":53361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:22:45.000Z","msg":"M記個招牌同形象係咪真係支持human rights架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1554ac13fafc6084bcddae10e1156078fd8b8cb","tid":1503773,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:15:18.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"c90578e93d6347a727bc9bd7e6da904a665ec750","tid":1503773,"uid":53361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:15:41.000Z","msg":"冇錯<br />\n中港M記係中信有經營權<br />\n但個品牌一樣係M記<br />\n而M記個招牌同形象係咪真係支持human rights架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n麥當勞作為國際大公司<br />\n又係美國股市上市<br />\n仲要係自己web page Missions &amp; Values 到寫 Respect Human Rights<br />\n<a href=\"https://corporate.mcdonalds.com/corpmcd/scale-for-good/our-people-and-communities/respecting-human-rights.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.mcdonalds.com%2Fcorpmcd%2Fscale-for-good%2Four-people-and-communities%2Frespecting-human-rights.html&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUMRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=92b1492c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://corporate.mcdonalds.com/corpmcd/scale-for-good/our-people-and-communities/respecting-human-rights.html</a><br />\n但係又比六折犯人道罪既香港警察<br />\n行為同說話都唔同既<br />\n咁係咪應該問下總公司佢地個立埸係咩呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nsend email去呢到<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mcdonalds.com/press/press-contacts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mcdonalds.com%2Fpress%2Fpress-contacts&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUMRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=dce380e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mcdonalds.com/press/press-contacts</a><br />\n美國巴絲可以直接打電話去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}